Project structure
=================

doc/samples sample csv files

trunk/html html layout

trunk/phpapp php application

Project frameworks and libraries
===================
## Server: 
#### PHP
[Silex](http://silex.sensiolabs.org/) - microframework

### Client:

[Angularjs](https://angularjs.org/) - js framework

[dropzonejs](http://www.dropzonejs.com/) - drag and drop support

### SDK
Humanity SDK

Deploy tutorial
===============
1. run ```php composer.phar install``` in ```trunk/phpapp``` folder
2. make ```conf.php``` file in ```trunk/phpapp/config``` folder (just copy it from ```conf.php.sample```) and set there valid configs (client_id, etc.)
3. config ```trunk/phpapp/config/validator.json``` file for proper column validation  

Requirenments
===============
1. PHP >= 5.4
